    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride. It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really solid shape for its next owner! It runs like a dream and has been well-cared for over the years, making it a perfect choice if you're looking for something dependable and clean without the 'brand new' price tag. It's ready for its next adventure\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
