      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my ride! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this car, and it has been such a reliable companion for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next big adventure with you. I\u2019ve taken great care of it and I\u2019m looking to find it a wonderful new home as soon as possible, so I've priced it to move! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive. Can't wait to chat!",
      "price": 28900.0,
