      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and the factory M-Variable differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for long-term structural integrity. The suspension retains its OEM MacPherson strut/multi-link geometry with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the car shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with its 'good' status, but mechanically, the compression across all six cylinders remains within factory spec. A pure analog experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 32500.0,
